name: add
label: tf.add(a,b)
description:
Adds two tf.Tensors element-wise, A + B. Supports broadcasting. 
 We also expose tf.addStrict which has the same signature as this op and asserts that a and b are the same shape (does not broadcast).

parameters.name: b
parameters.label: b
parameters.description: The second tf.Tensor to add. Must have the same type as a.
